  "description": "领域内核：统一 Id、范式基类与 CQRS/ES/EDA 契约（零依赖）",
  "keywords": [
    "domain-kernel",
    "cqrs",
    "es",
    "eda",
    "ddd",
    "isolation"
  ],
  "license": "MIT",
